ne an\napproximate time-scale on which the star reappears in the sparse region, i.e. a\n\"waiting\" time-scale for observers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Apr 2018 01:30:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 8 May 2018 18:36:38 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 8 Jun 2018 12:02:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-12"}
