eling spectroscopy curves\nreveal that these spin-fluctuation modes can be triggered by tunneling\nelectrons, opening up potential applications also for paramagnetic adatoms.\nLastly, an overview of the outstanding issues and future directions is given.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Apr 2018 15:08:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-29"}
